enb_long_title: United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change: Twenty-Second Session of the Subsidiary Bodies
section_title: REGISTRY SYSTEMS UNDER THE KYOTO PROTOCOL
sentences: Murray Ward (New Zealand) chaired informal consultations on Monday, with delegates considering short draft conclusions.
Discussions focused on the process and the timing of the indicative schedule for developing the international transaction log (ITL).
A longer revised draft text was circulated on Monday evening.
